  <!-- ─── TAB: OVERVIEW ─── -->
  <div id="tab-overview" class="guide-section active">
    <div class="info-box">
      <strong style="color:var(--accent);">Luồng hoạt động tổng thể:</strong>
      <div class="arch-diagram" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <div class="arch-node">📤 Upload<br><small style="font-weight:400;color:#8888aa;">File / URL / Drive</small></div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="arch-node">🖥️ App Server<br><small style="font-weight:400;color:#8888aa;">Node.js / VPS</small></div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="arch-node">⚙️ Encode Worker<br><small style="font-weight:400;color:#8888aa;">FFmpeg / HLS</small></div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="arch-node">📦 Storage Server<br><small style="font-weight:400;color:#8888aa;">SFTP / R2</small></div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="arch-node">☁️ CDN<br><small style="font-weight:400;color:#8888aa;">Cloudflare</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:16px;">
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text-primary);">🖥️ App Server (VPS)</div>
        <ul style="font-size:13px;color:#b0b0d0;line-height:1.9;padding-left:18px;">
          <li>Node.js web app — quản lý video, user, server</li>
          <li>Tiếp nhận upload (file local, URL, Google Drive)</li>
          <li>Giao tiếp với encode workers qua HTTP</li>
          <li>Quản lý queue, retry logic</li>
          <li>Phục vụ giao diện admin và player embed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text-primary);">⚙️ Encode Worker</div>
        <ul style="font-size:13px;color:#b0b0d0;line-height:1.9;padding-left:18px;">
          <li>Server riêng — Node.js + FFmpeg</li>
          <li>Nhận file từ App, encode sang HLS (360p → 1080p)</li>
          <li>Upload HLS qua SFTP lên Storage Server</li>
          <li>Báo callback về App khi xong</li>
          <li>Nhiều workers = encode song song = nhanh hơn</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text-primary);">📦 Storage Server (Hetzner)</div>
        <ul style="font-size:13px;color:#b0b0d0;line-height:1.9;padding-left:18px;">
          <li>Dedicated server / Storage Box Hetzner</li>
          <li>Chứa toàn bộ file HLS (.m3u8, .ts)</li>
          <li>Kết nối qua SFTP (IP:22)</li>
          <li>Nginx phục vụ HLS cho CDN</li>
          <li>Cloudflare R2 cũng được hỗ trợ</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text-primary);">☁️ CDN (Cloudflare)</div>
        <ul style="font-size:13px;color:#b0b0d0;line-height:1.9;padding-left:18px;">
          <li>Cache HLS segments từ Storage Server</li>
          <li>Giảm tải cho Storage, tăng tốc độ phát</li>
